  "In Separate mode, this is the full API response. In Together mode, this is the extracted JSON block that was stripped from the AI's narrative response.": "Im Getrennten die vollständige Antwort. Im Zusammen der extrahierte JSON.",
  "The AI writes its normal response, then appends tracker JSON at the end. ScenePulse automatically extracts and hides the JSON.": "KI schreibt Antwort und hängt JSON an. ScenePulse extrahiert und versteckt.",
  "If the AI omits the tracker payload, ScenePulse can automatically run a separate API call to recover. Requires a connection profile to be configured.": "Wenn die KI Daten weglässt, kann ScenePulse automatisch wiederherstellen. Profil erforderlich.",
  "Dramatic": "Dramatisch",
  "Intense": "Intensiv",
  "Comedic": "Komisch",
  "Twist": "Wendung",
  "Exploratory": "Erkundend",
  "None suggested yet": "Noch keine Vorschläge",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Nach der Antwort generiert ein stiller Aufruf den JSON. ~250–300s/Nachricht.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Ein API-Aufruf — ~100–120s",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Kein Profilwechsel — kein Löschrisiko",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ KI hat vollen narrativen Kontext",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× schneller als Getrennt",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Verwendet Tokens vom Hauptbudget (~1.700)",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ Kann Erzähllänge leicht reduzieren",
  "✓ Clean responses — narrative never token-competes with tracker": "✓ Saubere Antworten — keine Token-Konkurrenz",
  "✓ Dedicated token budget for tracker output": "✓ Dediziertes Token-Budget für Tracker",
  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ Kann anderes Profil/Preset verwenden",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Zwei API-Aufrufe — 2–3× langsamer",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s Totzeit zwischen Aufrufen",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ bei 8 Msgs — auf 3–4 reduzieren",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Profilwechsel kann Nachrichtenlöschung verursachen",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Bettet vorherigen Snapshot ein (~1.9K) außer bei 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Wie viele aktuelle Nachrichten einbeziehen.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Nur Getrennter Modus — Zusammen nutzt STs Kontext.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Am schnellsten. Für 1-zu-1-Szenen (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Ausgewogen. Für die meisten Szenen (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Bessere Kontinuität für komplexe Szenen (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Maximaler Kontext aber langsamer und teurer",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Größter Geschwindigkeitsfaktor. Bei 8 Msgs ~10K — Verdopplung verdoppelt die Zeit. 3–4 reduziert 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Nur Getrennter Modus.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Wiederholungen bei ungültigem JSON.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Für JSON auf GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Bettet Szenen-Snapshots in den Kontext ein. Nur Getrennt. Tracker erhält immer den vorherigen.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Jeder Snapshot +~1.9K. 0 eliminiert. 1 für Kontinuität. Über 1 selten nützlich.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Als unsichtbarer Kontext — autoritative Hintergrundinformation.",
  "Appears as if the user said it — some models respond more attentively.": "Erscheint als Benutzeraussage — Modelle reagieren aufmerksamer.",
  "Appears as previous AI output — can reinforce the AI's own memory but may confuse some models.": "Als vorherige KI-Ausgabe — kann Gedächtnis stärken aber verwirren.",
  "Separate generation runs an isolated API call — it needs lorebook context injected since ST won't provide it automatically.": "Getrennte Generierung ist ein isolierter Aufruf — benötigt Lorebook.",
  "Together mode uses the normal generation — ST already injects lorebooks into context, so including them here would be redundant.": "Zusammen-Modus nutzt normale Generierung — ST injiziert bereits.",
